oe f\u00e6rre billetter i \u00e5r enn i fjor, men inntektene er likevel st\u00f8rre i \u00e5r, med ni millioner kroner mot fjor\u00e5rets 8,4 millioner.", "- Vi hadde flere dyre billetter i \u00e5r, spesielt for \u00abThe Veil of the Temple\u00bb og Sting. Samtidig hadde vi mange gratisarrangement, sier direkt\u00f8r for festivalen, Petter Myhr."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "60cc8656e7e4cca19d1ac7f261edd4a40a16d667e9be3c3541b894e4fa65b9e8"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-29T23:58:19.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Olavsfestdagene gj\u00f8r lurt i \u00e5 satse mer p\u00e5 kirkemusikk og \u00e5ndelig debatt, mener Erik Hillestad, Eystein Sandvik og Alf van der Hagen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article11379949.ece/lxoc5o/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Veil_of_the_Temple011%20(2).jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/2a64cc0d0c8346047a87dd17dd4c37bc59a14406.jpg?5935c82f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Fikk suksess med kirkelig fokus -adressa.no", "Ivaretar tradisjonen", "- B\u00f8r v\u00e6re enda dristigere", "St\u00f8rre inntekter, f\u00e6rre billetter"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "2a64cc0d0c8346047a87dd17dd4c37bc59a14406"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["anmeldelser", "det skjer", "film", "musikk", "tv", "museum", "scene", "spill"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "anmeldelser,det skjer,film,musikk,tv,museum,scene,spill"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["klassisk musikk", "enda dristigere", "festival", "\u00f8kt fokus", "kirkelig fokus", "f\u00e6rre billetter", "\u00e5rets program", "of the"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["the veil", "kirkelig kult